      "content": "but i already tried letting go. i tried just \"stepping away\" from work and stuff, but the feeling doesn't go away. none of it helps. it just feels like the loop is built into me. no matter what i do, i end up right back in this same dark place. it's like the only way to actually stop the cycle is to just... stop everything. permanently.",
